name: Ambigrammatic Figure #0009 (Card 06)
description: The grotesque face in this GIF is an "ambigram": an image that is legible both upside-down and right-side-up. Created with a machine learning system, this is one of 55 works in the Ambigrammatic Figure Series (2020) by Golan Levin (@golan) with Lingdong Huang (@LingdongH).
